│ vector_insert uses the sub-vector value produced by a load/gather that        │
│ appears later in the block.\n\n   In short: setInsertPointAfterBundle(E) only │
│ considers E; for gather nodes that insert sub-vectors from other entries, we  │
│ must emit after the latest of E and all combined entries to preserve          │
│ dominance.\n\n4. Proposed Edit Point(s)\n   - File:                           │
